item.title: About me
item.description: Welcome to my blog! I write about software engineering – my personal projects, projects I find interesting, explanations of some LeetCode problems, concepts and topics that don’t have enough explanation online. Feel free to check out my pages in other locations of the Internet: Personal website: soon™ Instagram: @ykozyr LinkedIn: Yehor Kozyr LeetCode: Sne4kers GitHub: Sne4kers Contact: soon™, for now use LinkedIn
